Bayan da aka tabbatar da cewa an dage zaben domin ya zabi wanda zai zama babban lauya, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya ga kansa don zaben da ke tafe saboda Republican Party na fuskantar hadarin rasa ikon da ke kan majalisar idan aka yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
Wace sa'a ce taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da kuma yadda za ku iya kallon ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare na ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube kai tsaye.
Da alama Trump zai tattauna batun wannan makon na dan takarar da ya dace a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar matsi bayan da aka zarge shi da aikata lalata da kuma hasashen cewa za a dage zaben majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban burin wannan taron na jama'a shi ne ya taimaka wa jam'iyyar Republican ta samu karfin gwiwa a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, a cikin kamfen din Trump ya ce tarurrukan da za a yi a mako mai zuwa za su "tabbatar da 'yan sa kai da magoya bayansu yayin da' yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar dattawa", a cewar Reuters.
"Gudanar da majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban, don haka zai yi yawan tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi a yayin da muke fuskantar kakar yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda ya ce ba za a bayyana sunansa ba.
An shirya taron a filin wasa na Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, kuma ana sa ran taron na wannan maraice zai jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma Pittsburgh", in ji jaridar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyararsa ta biyu a cikin wata guda zuwa West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin 100.
