Masu Kirkirar Yanar Gizon Duniya Suna Shirya Sabuwar Yanar Gizon Don Yiwa Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani da ke kokarin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon, da kuma Google.
Sabon aikinsa, Inrupt, kamfani ne da aka gina a kan wani babban dandamali mai suna Solid wanda Berners-Lee ya kirkiro.
Solid ya ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda za a ba damar samun damar zuwa ga kowane irin bayani.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman tare da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu fara yanzu", in ji wanda ya fara aikin.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app yana amfani da fasaha na Solid wanda ke ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar "aikin ajiya na sirri na kan layi" ko POD.
Wannan ajiya na iya ƙunshe da jerin lambobi, jerin ayyuka, kalandarku, kundin waƙoƙi, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin wata hanyar bincike kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da wannan ajiyar bayanan sirri ta yanar gizo shi ne cewa yana da cikakken iko kan mai amfani ya ga wane irin bayanai za su iya samun dama.
A cikin kamfanonin, an san shi da "karfafawa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar kafa Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce a samar da albarkatu, tsari da kuma kwarewar da ta dace domin taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani tsarin tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu ma'aikatan ci gaba da aka ba da izini don yin aikin, da kuma masu sa kai na masu coding.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen sarrafa kansu ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da wani canji na gaba ɗaya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su zai juya baya cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A cikin wani rubutu da aka wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi da tsarin kasuwanci don taimakawa wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizo da aka gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Sadarwar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya zama sanannen murya a cikin muhawarar rashin nuna bambanci.
Ko da a lokacin da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da kuma Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina matukar fatan za a samu cigaban yanar gizo", Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
