Kashi ashirin cikin ɗari na daliban sun ce suna da asusun ajiyar "mafi muhimmanci" da za su nuna wa iyayensu
Ɗaya daga cikin yara biyar - wasu ma 'yan shekara 11 - sun kafa asusun sada zumunta da suka ɓoye wa manya.
Wani bincike da aka yi wa ɗaliban makarantar sakandare 20,000 ya nuna yadda asusun "Insta" na karya - wanda ake amfani da shi wajen yin amfani da hotuna a shafin Instagram - ke bunkasa.
Labarin ya kara tayar da hankali game da yadda take sanya hotunan batsa.
Kashi 20 cikin 100 na daliban sun ce suna gudanar da asusun ajiyarsu na farko da aka share domin nuna wa iyayensu, yayin da suke da asusun ajiyarsu na sirri.
Wata uwa da ta gano wani shafin sirri na 'yarta 'yar shekara 13 ta sami wani matashi yana neman wani ya "yi mata fyaɗe".
Binciken da Digital Awareness UK da kuma HMC na makarantu masu zaman kansu suka gudanar ya gano cewa kashi 40 cikin dari na dalibai 'yan shekara 11 zuwa 18 suna da bayanan sirri guda biyu, inda rabin su suka ce suna da asusun sirri.
Shugaban HMC, Mike Buchanan ya ce: "Yana da damuwa ga matasa da yawa da suke ƙoƙarin ƙirƙirar wani wuri a kan layi wanda iyayensu da malamai ba za su iya samunsa ba".
Eilidh Doyle za ta zama "muryar 'yan wasa" a hukumar wasannin Scotland
Eilidh Doyle ta samu shiga a hukumar 'yan wasa ta Scotland a matsayin darakta mara zartarwa a taron shekara shekara na hukumar.
Doyle shi ne dan wasan tsere da tseren da aka fi ba da lambar yabo a Scotland kuma shugaban Ian Beattie ya bayyana wannan a matsayin babbar dama ga wadanda ke jagorantar wasanni don amfana daga kwarewarsa a duniya a cikin shekarun da suka gabata.
"An girmama Eilidh sosai a duk faɗin Scotland, Ingila, da kuma al'ummomin wasannin motsa jiki na duniya kuma mun yi imanin wasannin motsa jiki a Scotland za su amfana sosai ta hanyar shigar da ita cikin kwamitin", in ji Beattie.
Doyle ya ce: "Ina aiki a matsayin murya ga 'yan wasa kuma ina fatan in iya ba da gudummawa da gaske kuma in taimaka wajen jagorancin wasanni a Scotland".
Dan wasan Amurka, wanda ya lashe tseren 200 da kuma 400 a gasar Olympics na 1996 a Atlanta a cikin lambobin zinare na Olympics guda hudu kuma yanzu ya zama masanin wannan BBC, yanzu ba zai iya tafiya ba bayan ya sha wahala daga kamuwa da cutar ischemic.
Ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Kwanan wata da suka wuce na samu bugun jini.
Ba zan iya tafiya ba.
Likitoci sun ce lokaci ne kawai zai nuna ko zan iya samun sauƙi da kuma yadda zan iya samunsa.
Ya zama abin gajiya a gare ni in dawo cikin koshin lafiya, in koyi yadda ake tafiya, kuma a yau na yi aikin motsa jiki!
