An harbe wani mutum da bindiga a Ilfracombe
An harbe wani mutum da bindiga a kan hanyarsa ta komawa gida daga wani liyafar da ya je.
Mutumin da ya mutu yana da shekara 40 yana zaune a wani yanki a Oxford Grove, Ilfracombe, Devon, inda aka harbe shi da harsasai da dama a kirji, da ciki, da kuma hannaye.
Jami'an sun bayyana cewa harbin ya faru ne da misalin karfe 2:30 na safe, kuma an ce "aiki ne na bazata".
Ba wanda ya gan shi ya yi masa dukan tsiya.
Raunin da aka samu a lokacin ba na barazana ga rayuwarsa ba kuma 'yan sanda sun kawo shaidu da yawa.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun auku a ƙasar Indonisiya
Girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a sun yi sanadin mutuwar mutane 384 a kalla, in ji jami'an, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Rashin sadarwa ya sa jami'an agaji na fuskantar matsala wajen samun bayanai daga Donggala County, wani yanki da ke arewacin birnin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa da ta kai 7.5.
A Palu, bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da biranen Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala, a halin yanzu, yanki ne mai fadin kilomita 300 na gabar tekun a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan gundumar, wacce yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, an kiyasta cewa tana da mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Babban abin da ke kawo kuɗi a lardin Sulawesi ta Kudu shi ne kamun kifi da kuma noman dabbobi, musamman a bakin tekun Donggala.
Duk da haka, ma'adinan nickel suna da mahimmanci a lardin, ko da yake sun fi yawa a cikin Morowali, a gabar Sulawesi.
An rubuta a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa, bisa ga bayanan Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane fiye da 200 sun mutu a guguwar tsunami da ta auku a shekara ta 1938, kuma ɗarurruwan gidaje sun rushe.
A shekara ta 1996, mutane tara sun mutu a tsunami a yammacin Donggala.
A bangaren girgizar kasa, Indonesia tana kan Zoben Wuta na Pacific kuma saboda haka girgizar kasa za ta iya faruwa a kai a kai.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, manyan girgizar asa da tsunami sun faru kamar haka:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, Indonesia ta fuskanci wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske, a gabar tekun lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, wadda ta haifar da tsunami a kasashe 14, inda ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu sun kasance a Aceh.
A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, jerin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar Sumatra ta yamma.
A tsibirin Nias, da ke kusa da Sumatra, an yi wa mutane ɗarurruwa mutuwa.
2006: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami a kudancin tekun, kuma kusan mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ya auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 33 da ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Gundumar Pidie Jaya, Aceh, ta fuskanci girgizar kasa mai zurfi da ta haifar da lalacewa, da kuma fargaba daga mutanen da suka tuna da lalacewar da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
Ko da yake a wannan karon babu yiwuwar tsunami, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sakamakon rushewar ginin.
A shekara ta 2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta kashe mutane sama da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta yi awon gaba da gine-gine da yawa kuma ta kori dubban masu yawon bude ido.
An Kama Ɗan 'Yar Saratu Palin Saboda Ɓatacciyar Halinsa
An kama Palin, wanda shi ne ɗan fari na Sarah Palin, tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, a matsayin wanda aka kama a wani hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, hana rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida da kuma tsayayya da yunkurin kama shi, kamar yadda wani rahoto na 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska ya fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, a lokacin da wata mata da ta san wani ya kira 'yan sanda don ya ba da rahoton aikata laifi, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun matar.
An mika Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su, tare da biyan $500 ba tare da ba da belin ba, kamar yadda hukumar ta KTUU ta ruwaito.
Kamar yadda cibiyoyin labarai suka ruwaito, Palin ta halarci shari'ar a ranar Asabar, tana mai cewa "ba ta da laifi, kamar yadda ta tabbata" lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da kare kanta.
Palin na fuskantar laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda zai iya sa shi ya yi shekara guda a gidan yari da kuma tarar $250,000.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma tuhume shi da laifin aikata laifi na Class B, wanda ke da ɗaurin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai wa Palin ƙara ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da yin hari kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ita ce ta kira 'yan sanda don ta ba da rahoton zargin da ake yi na kai mata hari.
A yanzu haka, an shigar da karar zuwa Kotun Tsohon Sojan Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata, hana bayar da rahoto game da cin zarafin mata, da kuma mallakar bindigogi a cikin maye, wanda kuma ya shafi wannan lamarin.
Abokinta ya zarge ta da yin lalata da ita.
A shekara ta 2016, ƙungiyar masu ba da shawara ga tsofaffi ta zargi Sarah Palin cewa ɗanta yana fama da PTSD saboda aikin da ya yi a Iraki.
Tsunami da girgizar kasa a Indonesia: daruruwan sun mutu
A ranar Juma'a, an yi mummunar girgizar kasa a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia inda akalla mutane 384 suka mutu.
Girgizar ƙasa da ta kai 7.5 a ma'aunin Richter da ke da ƙarfin jawo tsunami ta hallaka dubban gidaje.
An yi hasarar wutar lantarki da kuma sadarwa, kuma an yi hasarar rayuka da yawa a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
An yi girgizar ƙasa a tsakiyar Sulawesi, a arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin ƙasar Indonesia.
Bidiyon da ke nuna irin mummunan bala'in da ya faru ya bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don yin bikin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palu a lokacin da tsunami ya tarwatsa bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York City, inda mutane takwas suka mutu -- hukuncin da ya hada da wanda ba a taba yi ba a jihar don aikata laifukan tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an zarge shi da aikata laifin kai hari da kuma fado da wata babbar motar haya da ya yi haya da ita daga Home Depot a kan masu tafiya da kafa da kuma masu kekuna a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan a watan Oktoba.
Don a yanke hukuncin kisa, dole ne masu gabatar da kara su bayar da shaidar cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya "sanadi" haifar da mummunar rauni, bisa ga takardar shaidar da aka gabatar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
A cikin takardar da aka rubuta a kotu, an ce waɗannan laifuffukan sun sa ya dace a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22, ciki har da kisan kai a kan zargin zamba, wanda ake amfani da shi a kotun tarayya a kan laifuka na aikata laifuka, da kuma aikata laifuffuka da kuma kokarin lalata wata mota.
A cewar mai gabatar da kara, harin ya bukaci "tsara da kuma shiri mai zurfi", wanda ya nuna cewa laifin Saipov ya aikata shi da "ban tsoro, zalunci, da kuma rashin mutunci".
An bayyana a cikin wasiƙar wasiƙa, "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, haɗari, da asara ga dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda abin ya shafa 'yan yawon bude ido ne 'yan kasar Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun wuce tun lokacin da Kotun Kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe.
A watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, Khalid Barnes, wanda aka tuhuma da kisan gillar da aka yi wa masu sayar da magunguna guda biyu, an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai.
A ƙarshe an yi kisa a kotun tarayya ta New York a shekara ta 1953, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka same su da laifin yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Baki shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe ma'auratan Rosenberg a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar bayanan da aka samu a kotu, Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna wata damuwa ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni da suka biyo bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce, sa'ad da aka tambaye shi game da abin da ya yi, ya ce ya yi farin ciki da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya kuma bayyana wa hukumomi cewa an yi masa harin ne bisa bidiyon da kungiyar IS ta dauka a wayar sa, kamar yadda ake zargi da shi.
Ya kuma bukaci a sanya tutar ISIS a dakinsa a asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya amsa da cewa ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da ake yi masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya bayyana "bacin rai a fili" kan hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"A ganinmu, yanke hukuncin kisa maimakon a karbi hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da ba da tabbacin ba zai kara wa mutanen da abin ya shafa tsawon rai ba", in ji Patton.
A baya, tawagar kare Saipov ta nemi mai gabatar da kara kada ya yanke hukuncin kisa.
Nigel Farage ne ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit, in ji 'yan majalisar Tory
Nigel Farage ya yi kira ga 'yan adawa su 'kaddamar da sojojin su' a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron masu ra'ayin Tory.
Tsohon shugaban na Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su ji zafin' Eurosceptics (ra'ayin da ke adawa da Tarayyar Turai) - saboda 'yar majalisa Theresa May ta ce ta shiga cikin tattaunawar da EU.
Wani mai goyon bayan jam'iyyar Conservative, Peter Bone, ya shaida wa masu zanga-zanga a Birmingham cewa, "Ya kamata Birtaniya ta fice" a yanzu idan Farage ya ci gaba da zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma duk da haka, ƙalubalen da May ke fuskanta na sulhunta kujerun da ta raba ya zama abin da magoya bayan Remain Tories suka yi a cikin zanga-zangar da aka yi a birnin don nuna rashin amincewa da Brexit.
Firayim Minista na kokarin kare shirinsa na sasantawa na Chequers don ya ci gaba da kasancewa a kan sa duk da hare-haren da Brexiteers, Remainers da EU ke kaiwa.
Allied al'ummai jaddada cewa zai tura gaba zuwa cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels, duk da samun mummunan koma-baya - da kuma tilasta Eurosceptics da kuma Labor dole a zabi tsakanin ta kunshin da kuma 'damuwa'.
Bone ya gaya wa mutanen da suka bar Solihull cewa yana so ya 'cire Chequers.
Ya ce Farage ya kamata ya nada wanda zai dauki nauyin tattaunawar da Brussels.
"Idan har yanzu shi ne mai kula da shi, za mu fita yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar mai suna Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "A shirye nake na goyi bayan Brexit, amma muna bukatar mu kawar da Chequers".
Ya ce, a nuna rashin amincewarsa da Tarayyar Turai: "Ba don mu yi yaƙi a yaƙin duniya ba ne don mu zama masu biyayya.
Muna son mu kafa dokoki a ƙasarmu.'
Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa ra'ayin jama'a na iya haifar da canji tun lokacin da aka yi zaben 2016: "Ra'ayin cewa tunanin mutanen Burtaniya ya canza kuma suna son yanayin da ya dace, ba gaskiya bane".
Andrea Jenkyns, wata 'yar Tory mai goyon bayan ficewar, wadda ta halarci wannan zanga-zangar, ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: 'A sauƙaƙe, ina so in ce: Ya Firai Minista, ka saurari mutanenka.
Chequers ba shi da farin jini a wurin jama'a, yayin da 'yan adawa ba za su zaɓe shi ba, saboda ba shi da farin ciki da jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutukarmu waɗanda suka fita kan titi da gaske kuma suka sa aka zaɓe mu a matsayi na farko.
Muna roƙon ka ka cire Chequers dinka ka fara sauraronmu.'
A wata sanarwa da aka aika wa May, ya kara da cewa: "Firai minista na rike mukaminsa idan aka cika alkawarin da ya yi".
Farage ya ce dole ne a yi wa 'yan siyasa zanga-zanga don su ji zafin wutar idan suna son yin watsi da sakamakon zaben 2016.
"A yanzu abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne amincewa tsakaninmu - jama'a - da kuma 'yan siyasarmu", in ji shi.
'Sun yi kokarin yin watsi da Brexit kuma a nan ne muke a yau, muna tabbatar musu cewa ba za mu bar ku ku yi hakan ba'
Ya kara da cewa a cikin wani sako ga taron jama'a masu farin ciki: 'Ina so ku sa 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke shirin yin watsi da Brexit, su ma su ji zafi.
Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasar da za su ci nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za su yi kasa a gwiwa ba har sai an samar da wata kasar Burtaniya mai cin gashin kanta, mai cin gashin kanta, mai alfahari.
A halin da ake ciki, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ta yawo a cikin birni na Birmingham kafin su yi zanga-zanga a cikin gari na tsawon sa'o'i biyu.
An ga wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya suna dauke da tutar Tories Against Brexit bayan da suka yi zanga-zangar karshen mako.
A wani bangare kuma, abokin aikinsa a ma'aikatar, Lord Adonis, ya yi ba'a ga 'yan Conservative a kan batun tsaro na manhajarsu a lokacin da aka fara taron.
"Waɗannan mutanen ne suka gaya mana cewa za su iya mallakar tsarin IT da kuma dukan fasahar Kanada, ko da menene, don iyakokin da ba za su iya yin karo ba, a cikin tsarin kasuwanci mara iyaka a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wane irin wasa ne.
Babu wani abin da ya fi kyau a cikin Brexit,' in ji ta.
Warren yana shirin yin wani babban fashin-baƙarya a zaben shugaban kasa
A Amurka, Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "ci gaba da takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa jam'iyyar Democrat ta Massachusetts ta bayyana makomarta a wani babban taro a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ya saba sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, ya yi takarar sake zabensa a watan Nuwamba a kan wakilin GOP na jihar, Geoff Diehl, mataimakin shugaban kamfen na 2016 na Trump a Massachusetts.
A cikin hasashen da ake yi a fadin kasar, an bayyana cewa zai iya adawa da Trump a shekarar 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne na 36 da aka yi da masu kada kuri'a, wanda aka yi a cikin tsarin zauren gari tun lokacin da Trump ya hau kujerar mulki.
Wani mai halarta ya tambaye shi ko yana da shirin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa da cewa lokaci ya yi "da mata za su shiga cikin Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma wannan ya hada da lokacin da mata ke kan gaba".
An kama wanda ya yi wannan harin na Sims, dan wasan LSU
A ranar Asabar ne 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, suka sanar da kama wanda ake zargi da harbin da ya yi sanadin mutuwar Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwallon kwando na LSU, a ranar Juma'a.
A ranar Talata, an kama wani mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, ɗan shekara 20, a wani taro da 'yan sanda suka yi a birnin Baton Rouge.
Sun fitar da bidiyon harbin da ya faru ranar Juma'a, inda wani mutum da aka gano yana neman taimako kamar yadda aka gani a cikin faifan.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, an gano Sims, mai shekara 20, an harbe shi kuma an kashe shi a kusa da harabar jami'ar Southern.
"Wayde Sims ya samu rauni ne a kan kansa kuma ya mutu", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda, Murphy J. Paul, ya shaida wa manema labarai a ranar Asabar, ta hanyar 247sports.
Wayde yana son ya kare abokinsa, sai Simpson ya harbe shi.
A lokacin da aka tambaye shi, Simpson ya ce yana wurin, ya riƙe makamin, kuma ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da ya yi wata hamayya ba kuma aka tsare shi a ofishin 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge na Gabas.
Dan wasan mai kafa 6 da inci 6 wanda ya girma a Baton Rouge, wannan shine Sims, ya buga wasanni 32 tare da farawa 10 a kakar da ta gabata kuma yana da kimanin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da kuma 2.9 a kowane wasa.
A ranar Litinin a Rasha, Lewis Hamilton ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya bayan da ya yi nasara a kan Sebastian Vettel
Dukkanin ya bayyana a lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya kasance a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar a cikin wasan kwaikwayo wanda zai kawo umarni ga tawagar Mercedes yana da babban rawa a cikin tseren.
Daga kan tsere, Bottas ya fara da kyau kuma ya kusan barin Hamilton saboda ya riƙe matsayinsa a farkon biyu kuma ya jawo Vettel don ya kai wa abokansa hari.
Vettel ya kasance na farko da ya shiga cikin rami kuma ya bar Hamilton ya shiga cikin taro a ƙarshen taron, wani abu da ya kamata ya zama mai ƙayyadewa.
Mercedes ta shiga bayan da ta yi zagayen farko kuma ta fita bayan Vettel, amma Hamilton ya ci gaba da tafiya bayan wasu tsere-tsere da suka nuna rashin son direban Ferrari ya bar ciki a cikin wani bangare na ciki ba tare da haɗarin tsere ba bayan sau biyu don tsere a kusurwar uku.
Max Verstappen ya fara a layin ƙarshe kuma ya kasance a cikin na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwar ranar haihuwar sa ta 21.
Ya ci gaba da jagorantar mafi yawan tseren saboda ya riƙe canjin taya don saurin kawo karshen kuma ya ɗauki matsayin Kimi Raikkonen na hudu.
A ƙarshe ya shiga cikin rami a zagaye na 44 amma ya kasa haɓaka saurinsa a zagaye na takwas da ya rage saboda Raikkonen ya ɗauki matsayi na huɗu.
Rana ce mai wuya, domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai ban mamaki a karshen mako kuma wani mutum na gaskiya ya bar ni.
"Kungiyar ta yi aiki mai ban mamaki don samun daya biyu", in ji Hamilton.
Wannan ba harshen jiki ba ne.
